articles.title: Jock Zonfrillo, MasterChef Australia host, found dead at age 46 - CBS News
articles.description: The father of four who was a judge on the popular TV cooking competition was found dead by police in Melbourne in the early hours of Monday.
articles.content: MasterChef Australia host Jock Zonfrillo has died at the age of 46, according to a message from his family and a statement from the broadcaster of the show. Zonfrillo, a Scottish-Australian father of… [+2393 chars]
